From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MXE
Date: Sun, 31 May 2026 10:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/1] Fix Windows.h include case

MinGW-w64 on case-sensitive filesystems requires lowercase <windows.h>.

---
 kirigami-plasmadesktop-integration/animationspeedprovider.cpp | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/kirigami-plasmadesktop-integration/animationspeedprovider.cpp b/kirigami-plasmadesktop-integration/animationspeedprovider.cpp
index 1234567..89abcdef 100644
--- a/kirigami-plasmadesktop-integration/animationspeedprovider.cpp
+++ b/kirigami-plasmadesktop-integration/animationspeedprovider.cpp
@@ -12,7 +12,7 @@
 
 #ifdef Q_OS_WIN
 #include <QCoreApplication>
-#include <Windows.h>
+#include <windows.h>
 #endif
 
 using namespace Qt::StringLiterals;
